   synonymy with M. albohirta (Brulle), M. albocincta Radoszkowski with
   cyanipennis Guerin-Meneville, M. rhodosiaca Rebmann and M. heinrichi
   (Tkalcu) with M. doriae Magretti, M. vicina Morawitz with M. giraudi, M.
   picicornis Morawitz and M. albocincta Perez with M. marginata, M.
